New Records: Nikola Jokić and Russell Westbrook became the first pair of teammates to record triple-doubles in the same game multiple times in the same season.
Key Match Events: Nikola Jokić recorded a triple-double with 35 points, 15 assists, and 12 rebounds.
Russell Westbrook recorded a triple-double with 25 points, 11 rebounds, and 10 assists.
